<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-11-0050 </DOCNO><TEXT>The Energy Performance Assessment (EPA) project to evaluate the benefitsof passive solar features in 40 occupied buildings - both domestic andnon-domestic - over a 3 to 4 year period is described, and whole buildingevaluation, fuel and energy performance and capital cost of the buildingand its principal components are discussed. Selected methodology, resources,and related programmes are considered.</TEXT></DOC>